6. To display a number equivalent to hex and octal quivalent and its square root:-

num = int(input("Enter a number : "))
print("Hexadecimal of " + str(num) + " : " + str(hex(num)))
print("Octadecimal of " + str(num) + " : " + str(oct(num)))
print("Square root of " + str(num) + " : " + str(num**0.5))

#Output:-
Enter a number : 100
Hexadecimal of 100 : 0x64
Octadecimal of 100 : 0o144
Square root of 100 : 10.0

7. To find area of traingle using heron's formula:-

a = int(input("Enter first side of triangle : "))
b = int(input("Enter second side of triangle : "))
c = int(input("Enter third side of triangle : "))
s = (a+b+c)/2
area = (s*(s-a)*(s-b)*(s-c))**0.5
print("Area of triangle + " + str(area))

#Output:-
Enter first side of triangle : 12
Enter second side of triangle : 18
Enter third side of triangle : 10
Area of triangle + 56.568542494923804

8. To find distance between two points:-

x1 = int(input("Enter the coordinates of x1 = "))
y1 = int(input("Enter the coordinates of y1 = "))
x2 = int(input("Enter the coordinates of x2 = "))
y2 = int(input("Enter the coordinates of y2 = "))
d = ((x1- x2)**2 + (y1-y2)**2)**0.5
print("Distance : " + str(d))

#Output:-
Enter the coordinates of x1 = 4
Enter the coordinates of y1 = 5
Enter the coordinates of x2 = 6
Enter the coordinates of y2 = 1
Distance : 4.47213595499958

9. To demonstrate relational operator:-

x = 10
y = 20
print(str(x) + " > " +str(y) + " = " +str(x>y) )
print(str(x) + " < " +str(y) + " = " +str(x<y) )
print(str(x) + " == "+str(y) + " = " +str(x==y) )
print(str(x) + " != "+str(y) + " = " +str(x!=y) )
print(str(x) + " >= "+str(y) + " = " +str(x>=y) )
print(str(x) + " <= "+str(y) + " = " +str(x<=y) )

#Output:- 
10 > 20 = False
10 < 20 = True
10 == 20 = False
10 != 20 = True
10 >= 20 = False
10 <= 20 = True

10. To calculate area and circumference of circle:-

r = int(input("Enter radius of circle : "))
area = 3.14 *(r**2)
circum = 2 * 3.14 * r
print("Area of circle : " + str(area))
print("Circumference of circle : ", circum )

#Output:- 
Enter radius of circle : 7
Area of circle : 153.86
Circumference of circle :  43.96

